metadata.name: Air Jesus
metadata.description:
Sick and tired of your worn-out kicks? 
Look no further than the Air Jesus, fresh from the gates of heaven! 

These limited-time kicks give you the power to walk on water, turn water into wine (great at parties), and even come back to life 3 days later if you die while wearing them.

Gamers, listen up! The Air Jesus will also give you +10 holy damage to all your skills.

But that's not all!

Order now and you might just be the lucky winner of a special edition pair, signed by Jesus himself. Don't miss out on this heavenly footwear! Get your pair of Air Jesus today.
